title: Mega Bots.apk
description:
Mega Bots are everywhere. Alien technology has invaded earth. Huge Robots are sent from Distant planets to kill everyone. You are the pilot of one of these heavy terror machine. Kill Anything and Everything in your path. Show no mercy. Level the ground with fury and power of your Mega Bot and make place for the alien race to thrive on Earth. Everyone tries to be hero,lets try something new with the killer Mega Bots.
Features
--------------
1. Breathtaking Graphics
Experience the action in stunning graphics! Witness the dazzling display of each Mega Bot's unique skills!
2. Collection of Robots! 
Buy Robots from many Bots with different Metallic properties of Steel,Gold,Alloy e.t.c!
3. Endless Fun! 
An endless game is much more fun than ending,Kill and move as far as possible with these heavy terror machine!
4. Rocking Guns 
Unleash your Robo fury with our 50Caliber guns, Rocket Launchers and Laser Shots.
